09:00.497 --> 09:01.875
Yay!

09:06.317 --> 09:07.652
That was awesome!

09:07.653 --> 09:08.888
Hey, where are we?

09:08.889 --> 09:10.924
Peter, you've lost
your Christmas spirit,

09:10.925 --> 09:14.695
