to "Christmas Past" to find it.

09:14.696 --> 09:16.029
Oh, wow.

09:16.030 --> 09:18.865
Th-This is my old house from
when I was a little kid.

09:18.866 --> 09:20.200
That's right, Peter.

09:20.201 --> 09:24.204
